Privacy Policy
Effective Date: 01 September 2023
Thank you for choosing SkyORB , the ultimate astronomy app that respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your personal information when you use our mobile application, SkyORB (“the App”). By downloading, installing, or using the App, you consent to the practices described in this Privacy Policy.
Information We Collect
The App does not collect any personal information from users. We do not require you to create an account or provide any personal details. The App operates in full compliance with Apple’s privacy policies and guidelines.
No User Tracking or Analytics
We do not engage in any form of user tracking or analytics. The App respects your privacy and does not monitor, store, or share any data about your activities within the App.
No Data Stored on Servers
The App  does not save or store any user data on our servers. All data related to your usage of the App remains on your device.
Third-Party Services
The App may integrate with third-party services such as the Apple App Store for download and updates. Please be aware that these third-party services have their own privacy policies, and we recommend reviewing their terms and conditions for further information.
Children’s Privacy
The App is not intended for use by children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you are a parent or guardian and believe that your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us immediately at contact@skyorb.app, and we will delete such information from our records.
Security
The App prioritizes the security of your personal information. We implement reasonable security measures to protect against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction of data.
Changes to this Privacy Policy
We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be effective immediately upon posting the revised Privacy Policy, and the date of the last update will be indicated at the top of the policy. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically to stay informed about how we are protecting your information.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at contact @ skyorb dot app
